Enum Class EjbcaEventTypes

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<EjbcaEventTypes>
org.ejbca.core.ejb.audit.enums.EjbcaEventTypes
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<EjbcaEventTypes>, Constable, org.cesecore.audit.enums.ConstantType<org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType>, org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType
public enum EjbcaEventTypes extends Enum<EjbcaEventTypes> implements org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType
EJBCA specific security audit event types, for audit using CESecore's audit log. These event types extend the list of already existing event types of CESeCore.
